scenes.description: Pre-show slideshow showcasing fan messages and illustrations for the hololive English 2nd Concert - Breaking Dimensions.
Breaking News announcement from FuRyu regarding new hololive plushies coming to Round 1 in the US.
Continuation of the Breaking News with more details about the hololive campaign at Round 1 starting in October 2024.
Further fan messages and art displayed on the screen while waiting for the concert to start.
Visitor attention notice providing guidelines on flashing lights and cheering.
Merchandise showcase for official concert goods like T-shirts, towels, and fans.
Long-running slideshow of fan support messages until the end of the clip.
